## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

```bash
# Setup
git clone https://github.com/jagadeesh32/cello.git
cd cello
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install maturin pytest

# Build
maturin develop

# Test
pytest tests/ -v

# Lint
cargo clippy
cargo fmt
```

